user.biography: WHERE ANIMALS COME FIRST ❤️ Brolga & Tahnee - wildlife carers 🦘We rescue & raise orphaned kangaroos. Meet our roos on tour. Home of Kangaroo Dundee 🦘

node.text:
Thanks for all your kindness to us Aussies. Please visit us. We can’t wait to see you 🧡

Repost: @australia ❤️
We want to send our mates around the world a big thank you for all your love and support. We hope you will come visit soon!

node.text: Hello to you from our sweet Wendy 💖 Kangaroos generally don’t ‘talk’ much…mainly just mum and baby calling one another when baby is out of the pouch. But our Wendy likes to say hi each day.

node.text: Teddy loves being groomed by his good buddy Cindy-Lou. 💕 Even though they are different kangaroo types, a Red and a Euro, they grew up together and are very close. Kangaroos are very affectionate and regularly spend time grooming one another.
